{"tid":1617693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"太古康山一役後感: 念力語言攻勢要轉型, 反客為主","createTime":"2019-10-04T01:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T01:49:26.000Z","uid":265638,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0c947fa2226da1b18a509f58408fa603a91fa3c0","tid":1617693,"uid":265638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:15:30.000Z","msg":"琴晚經過太古康山見識到港島式抗爭<br />\n香港島嘅朋友喺首都榜應該敬陪末座<br />\n但係講到念力語言攻擊就真係哎交王<br />\n<br />\n鵪鶉有鵪鶉嘅好, 連水樽都唔會掟<br />\n班狗真係冇乜藉口開拖拉人, 成班企喺路口度佈防<br />\n一開始都係用基本對白、肥媽歌、叫佢哋返狗竇等等<br />\n班狗都應該有曬抗體無反應<br />\n<br />\n跟住就開始有好多元化對白<br />\n- 我交咁多稅你班撚樣企定定喺度俾我𨳒夠先好返狗竇, 郁親正契弟, 睇下我地長氣定你地襟𨳒<br />\n- 你老母生你出嚟咁犯賤企喺街度俾人𨳒嘅慰安狗<br />\n- 多謝阿sir madam企出嚟代表班高層俾我地發洩下<br />\n- 唔好呃OT錢啦, 企一世都住唔到太古城架<br />\n<br />\n而家鬥勇武未必個個得<br />\n幾百個街坊圍住𨳒做成嘅心理傷害唔差得過肉體傷害"},{"pid":"11eb04c49a1e9544fa78f87657963ae43cd86099","tid":1617693,"uid":69741,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"企一世都住唔到太古城架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d2dc6a03fff6020bb5c7bccf8b810a0da9cbc5","tid":1617693,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:30.000Z","msg":"Wow"},{"pid":"8bbb98e23950f0545660b0edc05ae0d141562f2c","tid":1617693,"uid":268547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"有學識係唔同d"},{"pid":"704bfd87f887bc2c8328547acf83df0a5c7cc140","tid":1617693,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11eb04c49a1e9544fa78f87657963ae43cd86099","tid":1617693,"uid":69741,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:16:34.000Z","msg":"企一世都住唔到太古城架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im